---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: AI-Powered Engineering Studio
description: NEXT3LABS is a Singapore-based AI-powered engineering studio. We build and run the high-stakes custom software businesses depend on — engineering excellence since 2016, AI-adapted for 2025.
permalink: /
bodyClass: v3
extraHead: |
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&family=Manrope:wght@700;800&family=JetBrains+Mono&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Material+Symbols+Outlined:opsz,wght,FILL,GRAD@24,400,0,0&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/v3.css">
---

<!-- ── Nav ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<nav class="v3-nav">
  <div class="v3-wrap">
    <a class="v3-nav__brand" href="/">
      <img src="/assets/images/next3labs-logo.png" alt="NEXT3LABS logo">
      <span>NEXT3LABS</span>
    </a>
    <div class="v3-nav__links">
      <a href="#capabilities">Studio</a>
      <a href="#principles">Approach</a>
      <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>
    </div>
    <div class="v3-nav__meta">
      Location &amp; History<br>
      <strong>Singapore · since {{ site.foundingYear }}</strong>
    </div>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ── Hero ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="v3-hero">
  <div class="v3-wrap v3-hero__grid">
    <div>
      <span class="v3-eyebrow">{{ site.descriptor }}</span>
      <h1>We build and run the <span class="accent">software businesses depend on.</span></h1>
      <p class="v3-hero__sub">High-stakes custom software, built and operated at the speed of AI. Singapore-based, engineering excellence since {{ site.foundingYear }}, AI-adapted for 2025.</p>
      <div class="v3-hero__ctas">
        <a class="v3-btn v3-btn--light" href="/contact/">Start a project</a>
        <a class="v3-btn v3-btn--ghost" href="#principles">Our approach</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="v3-terminal">
      <div class="v3-terminal__glow" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="v3-terminal__body">
        <div class="v3-terminal__dots" aria-hidden="true"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
        <div class="v3-terminal__lines">
          <div><span class="num">01</span>initializing studio environment...</div>
          <div><span class="num">02</span>loading <span class="hl">ai-augmented workflows</span></div>
          <div><span class="num">03</span>uptime since {{ site.foundingYear }}</div>
          <div><span class="num">04</span><span class="v3-cursor" aria-hidden="true"></span></div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="v3-terminal__badge">
        <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:18px;" aria-hidden="true">verified</span>
        Operating since {{ site.foundingYear }}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── Ticker strip ────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<div class="v3-strip">
  <div class="v3-wrap">
    <p>Singapore-based · operating since {{ site.foundingYear }} · AI-adapted engineering · built and run in production</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ── Core principles ─────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="v3-section v3-section--surface" id="principles">
  <div class="v3-wrap">
    <div class="v3-section__head">
      <p class="v3-kicker">Process &amp; Philosophy</p>
      <h2>Core principles</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="v3-cards v3-cards--3">
      <div class="v3-card">
        <div class="v3-card__num">01</div>
        <h3>AI-powered leverage</h3>
        <p>The output of a team, the overhead of one. We use modern AI tools to accelerate development without sacrificing quality, starting from 2025.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="v3-card">
        <div class="v3-card__num">02</div>
        <h3>Build AND run</h3>
        <p>We operate what we ship — no hand-off, no disappearing. We remain accountable for the performance and uptime of your systems.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="v3-card">
        <div class="v3-card__num">03</div>
        <h3>No lock-in</h3>
        <p>We integrate with the stack you already run. Our goal is to augment your infrastructure, not force you into a proprietary ecosystem.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── Studio capabilities ─────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="v3-section" id="capabilities">
  <div class="v3-wrap">
    <div class="v3-section__head">
      <p class="v3-kicker">Capabilities</p>
      <h2>Studio capabilities</h2>
      <p class="v3-section__lead">Senior, AI-augmented engineering, operated in production.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="v3-cards v3-cards--4">
      <div class="v3-card v3-card--cap">
        <div class="v3-card__icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">api</span></div>
        <h3>Custom software &amp; APIs</h3>
        <p>Scalable backends and resilient internal tools designed for longevity.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="v3-card v3-card--cap">
        <div class="v3-card__icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">cloud_sync</span></div>
        <h3>Infrastructure &amp; DevOps</h3>
        <p>Cloud-native architecture and automated deployment pipelines that just work.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="v3-card v3-card--cap">
        <div class="v3-card__icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">shield_lock</span></div>
        <h3>Security &amp; maintenance</h3>
        <p>Continuous monitoring and proactive patching since {{ site.foundingYear }}.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="v3-card v3-card--cap">
        <div class="v3-card__icon"><span class="material-symbols-outlined" aria-hidden="true">smart_toy</span></div>
        <h3>AI &amp; automation</h3>
        <p>Intelligent workflows that eliminate manual overhead and improve accuracy.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── Legacy / Evolution ──────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="v3-section v3-section--surface">
  <div class="v3-wrap">
    <div class="v3-band">
      <div class="v3-legacy">
        <div>
          <p class="v3-legacy__kicker">Legacy</p>
          <h3>Founded {{ site.foundingYear }} — engineering systems that stand the test of time</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="v3-legacy__foot">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:18px;" aria-hidden="true">history_edu</span>
          9+ Years of Studio History
        </div>
        <span class="v3-legacy__ghost" aria-hidden="true">2016</span>
      </div>
      <div class="v3-legacy">
        <div>
          <p class="v3-legacy__kicker">Evolution</p>
          <h3>AI-adapted in 2025 — building the future at modern speeds</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="v3-legacy__foot">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:18px;" aria-hidden="true">bolt</span>
          Modern AI-augmented stack
        </div>
        <span class="v3-legacy__ghost" aria-hidden="true">25</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── Final CTA ───────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="v3-finalcta">
  <div class="v3-wrap">
    <div class="v3-finalcta__box">
      <h2>Have a system you can't afford to get wrong?</h2>
      <div class="v3-finalcta__ctas">
        <a class="v3-btn v3-btn--light" href="/contact/">Talk to us</a>
        <a class="v3-btn v3-btn--ghost" href="https://api.whatsapp.com/send/?phone={{ site.whatsapp }}&text&type=phone_number" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined" style="font-size:18px;" aria-hidden="true">chat</span> WhatsApp Us
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ── Footer ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<footer class="v3-footer">
  <div class="v3-wrap">
    <div class="v3-footer__top">
      <div class="v3-footer__brand">
        <strong>{{ site.company.legalName }}</strong>
        <p>
          Singapore based<br>
          UEN {{ site.company.uen }}<br>
          <a href="mailto:{{ site.contactEmail }}">{{ site.contactEmail }}</a>
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="v3-footer__col">
        <h4>Studio</h4>
        <a href="#principles">Approach</a>
        <a href="#capabilities">Capabilities</a>
        <a href="/contact/">Contact</a>
      </div>
      <div class="v3-footer__col">
        <h4>Focus</h4>
        <a href="#capabilities">Engineering</a>
        <a href="#principles">Operations</a>
        <a href="#principles">AI Leverage</a>
      </div>
      <div class="v3-status">
        <span class="label">Current Status</span>
        <span class="dot" aria-hidden="true"></span> Accepting New Projects
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="v3-footer__legal">
      <span>{{ site.company.legalName }}, Singapore, UEN {{ site.company.uen }}</span>
      <span>
        <a href="/privacy/">Privacy Policy</a> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
        <a href="/terms/">Terms of Service</a>
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
